{"id": "ChIJKabBNYC9woARrO9sX53t5gY", "rating": 3.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 218, "displayName": {"text": "heytea (Beverly Hills)", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJKabBNYC9woARrO9sX53t5gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tjMGNVUndialZ0U0MxbldtOXpaV3hCV2prMFdIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had the mango drink today and it was really delicious! The mango tasted very fresh with a strong fruity flavor. It was refreshing and not overly sweet. The combination of the tea and cream topping was perfect, smooth and well balanced. The staff were friendly and the service was fast. Overall, a great experience. I’ll definitely come back again — highly recommend the mango drinks to anyone who loves mango flavor!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had the mango drink today and it was really delicious! The mango tasted very fresh with a strong fruity flavor. It was refreshing and not overly sweet. The combination of the tea and cream topping was perfect, smooth and well balanced. The staff were friendly and the service was fast. Overall, a great experience. I’ll definitely come back again — highly recommend the mango drinks to anyone who loves mango flavor!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chen Yang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110140765368923244300/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhXcIK67vCMb4bOKYSDbuWQSCIVtCzYxiHIXRiC1eU4ybCDw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-24T02:46:47.539020746Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tjMGNVUndialZ0U0MxbldtOXpaV3hCV2prMFdIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tjMGNVUndialZ0U0MxbldtOXpaV3hCV2prMFdIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bd8035c1a629:0x6e6ed9d5f6cefac"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKabBNYC9woARrO9sX53t5gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SNVpsaGpTRmR4YTJsV2FrRXpNMTlwVUUxWGJrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "A wonderful experience from start to finish. The customer service at this Beverly Hills location is top-tier. The staff is extremely attentive, patient, and polite. Since it was my first time trying a few items, the barista took the time to genuinely recommend the sweetness levels and toppings based on my taste. The premium service perfectly matches the beautiful, clean aesthetic of the shop. Will definitely be a regular here!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A wonderful experience from start to finish. The customer service at this Beverly Hills location is top-tier. The staff is extremely attentive, patient, and polite. Since it was my first time trying a few items, the barista took the time to genuinely recommend the sweetness levels and toppings based on my taste. The premium service perfectly matches the beautiful, clean aesthetic of the shop. Will definitely be a regular here!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Y H", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108324140615821514198/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaFFJpK1o7cCKqA48XHlR5SBEtwh36ZA6HhyJ9ei_R6guVIwY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-23T03:51:16.128322222Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SNVpsaGpTRmR4YTJsV2FrRXpNMTlwVUUxWGJrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SNVpsaGpTRmR4YTJsV2FrRXpNMTlwVUUxWGJrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bd8035c1a629:0x6e6ed9d5f6cefac"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKabBNYC9woARrO9sX53t5gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JeE1XaHNkSHBwWjBaemNsVjVkR0pUZUZCbmRHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Heytea is a vibe. Super clean aesthetic of the shop with drinks to match. Got the green grape boom with no sugar and it is so refreshing. Well balanced aromatic green tea with fresh green grapes. Tastes like a healthy adult popsicle.\n\nHaven’t been a frequent patron of bubble tea shops because of all the garbage in the drinks, but the ingredients and drink combinations here are encouraging! The packaging is really sturdy and pretty. Def not eco friendly lol but will deliver well. Can’t wait to try more of their menu. The workers are really kind and helpful and efficient", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Heytea is a vibe. Super clean aesthetic of the shop with drinks to match. Got the green grape boom with no sugar and it is so refreshing. Well balanced aromatic green tea with fresh green grapes. Tastes like a healthy adult popsicle.\n\nHaven’t been a frequent patron of bubble tea shops because of all the garbage in the drinks, but the ingredients and drink combinations here are encouraging! The packaging is really sturdy and pretty. Def not eco friendly lol but will deliver well. Can’t wait to try more of their menu. The workers are really kind and helpful and efficient", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Yiwei Ling", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107522271304674618741/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWE5OQJaMryLy0gi1_oXxDhyBzAAkaJJq7d5xNi0QuCqBYeaV0e=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-24T23:23:17.861223798Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JeE1XaHNkSHBwWjBaemNsVjVkR0pUZUZCbmRHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JeE1XaHNkSHBwWjBaemNsVjVkR0pUZUZCbmRHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bd8035c1a629:0x6e6ed9d5f6cefac"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKabBNYC9woARrO9sX53t5gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oMWJEQXlPV3RJYTFkM2RWbHBPRTUxYURadGFWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Sooooo good!! Everything about these drinks is perfect. Boba TEXTURE & taste is PERFECT. Drinks are so fresh, tasty, & high quality. Will definitely be coming back to try more. This is like San Gabriel Valley level of boba, hard to find in LA.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Sooooo good!! Everything about these drinks is perfect. Boba TEXTURE & taste is PERFECT. Drinks are so fresh, tasty, & high quality. Will definitely be coming back to try more. This is like San Gabriel Valley level of boba, hard to find in LA.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Joshua Gonzales", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102825438611807993840/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7dQUoAz8Jh70csoG5PezQmBE0M52ydu5yGVlo7FAsx1_FIYYz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-08T21:57:20.487672745Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oMWJEQXlPV3RJYTFkM2RWbHBPRTUxYURadGFWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oMWJEQXlPV3RJYTFkM2RWbHBPRTUxYURadGFWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bd8035c1a629:0x6e6ed9d5f6cefac"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKabBNYC9woARrO9sX53t5gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCRlUwNXFPR1JqVWsxU01ucE5XRFV3Y1ZoQk5FRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Both drinks were incorrect and inconsistent with what HEYTEA usually serves at other locations. The Yingde Black Tea with mochi was missing. The Pistachio Cloud King Jasmine was completely different from how it’s normally made at other HEYTEA stores. There were not many orders, yet I still had to wait 25 minutes. This shows poor quality control, and the staff clearly need proper training. For the price, this level of inaccuracy and inconsistency is unacceptable", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Both drinks were incorrect and inconsistent with what HEYTEA usually serves at other locations. The Yingde Black Tea with mochi was missing. The Pistachio Cloud King Jasmine was completely different from how it’s normally made at other HEYTEA stores. There were not many orders, yet I still had to wait 25 minutes. This shows poor quality control, and the staff clearly need proper training. For the price, this level of inaccuracy and inconsistency is unacceptable", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Calista Huang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106799126697641178123/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoMaHa3GstWEcZMtFPmHOkGu01XS97tZvXp8bdd5_B8KyTwb4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-20T22:31:31.487849955Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCRlUwNXFPR1JqVWsxU01ucE5XRFV3Y1ZoQk5FRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCRlUwNXFPR1JqVWsxU01ucE5XRFV3Y1ZoQk5FRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bd8035c1a629:0x6e6ed9d5f6cefac"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJKabBNYC9woARrO9sX53t5gY/photos/AWCwydjFv2PSyYniEP0AjjtXtLMiGsURgyPfFp3ulXV_M0k39r8gMCFCGSeI75peL6_8wpZj1DTlXl6-U7NH3VrQ46BZHb0XoVfD2slTxm8sCLQ5oTn9W7DtR9eE40FbaUQrjNmpV-gC3h7qnKeGz17R_EwFiMRXW-dLsdzejup4DNtpBUV9NV5fdM9bDEfJvPSMX85pQOCzHz-V37egxxk8o35_p6C8VUdmWTBm45Z4nobGaPRrEk2azVgoyLIFkKw0ggMXbpxBr9ctbZYN2ik2_esEZBCK0E6TBcTYTGgwUEvm6NUIKS6AB3glrLwyDGVrL5gBqeY_QEMaDNwm2GIJ9DsqF5i-7ThjAr_2x2nfiZoDLFJhDC43EcTAgAFhhur6xq53-KVfFTMeafRiW7szLAwtzanQPTCRRGMwkAGEejxsHTVFBhFHkB8obu6Ss8rv", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 2700, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Esther Wu", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/117073325681478079572", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMjzkA1fOfw-33eE_lNp6JMVfw0c942c4gVeyEz5pU-1XGOC8=s100-p-k-no-